summaries: The document is an annual report (Form 10-K) for the fiscal year ending May 31, 2025, submitted by Oracle Corporation, a Delaware corporation with its principal executive offices located in Austin, Texas. The company's common stock trades under the symbol ORCL on the New York Stock Exchange. As of May 31, 2025, the aggregate market value of the voting stock held by non-affiliates was approximately $305.79 billion. The number of shares of common stock outstanding as of June 13, 2025, is 2,808,833,000. No errors were found in the financial statements that required correction or restatement, and Oracle Corporation is not considered a shell company. The company's definitive proxy statement for its 2025 annual meeting of stockholders will be filed with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission within 120 days of the end of the fiscal year.
